      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"7. NAIL IT jumped well from this draw last time and was prominent throughout before holding third (30.49) in a Class 2/3 at this track over 525m. Has been racing in stronger fields over the middle distance. Well worth another try. 5. BUSY WORK stretches out further in journey and is having her first try at the trip. Maiden off this draw but has run some good races. Looks a key chance on best figures. 4. TESS has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (31.01) in a Class 1/2 at this track. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and four minor placings to her credit. Has had the most experience over a staying distance in this field. 6. STORM'S THUNDER found the frame here last start and looks a top-three hope again.\",\"runners\":[7,5,4,6],\"exclusive\":false}",
